        body: `The tailgate starts in the group chat the Wednesday before. Who's bringing the grill, the meat, the alcohol, the chairs, the canopy. A moomz poll cuts through the chaos faster than any text thread. "Meat — burgers, brats, ribs, or all three?", "alcohol budget — $50, $100, $200, BYOB?", "canopy or no canopy?". Send the polls, get votes by Thursday night, and the maid-of-honor energy in the friend group can finally relax instead of texting 14 people separately for confirmations. The poll is the source of truth.`,
